item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: LedLamp-Direct
item.content:encoded:
Welcome to LEDLamp-Direct.com

LEDLamp-Direct.com is your supplier of energy-saving LED bulbs, tubes, utility lights and hardware. All for just a fraction of the price from a Big Box store! How? We buy quality LEDs in bulk and maintain a large on-hand inventory for most lamps and modules. We're centrally located in the United States, so we can provide quick deliveries at regular rates to 80% of the America.

Need some help?

If you are having some trouble deciding on what you need to get the job done, simply Contact Us for direct assistance. Well help you sort it out! We know LED lamps! If you know what you need but you cant find it here, get in touch with us for this, too. Odds are we can get it for you. And if there is no product that fits your exact needs, we can work with our suppliers to get you an LED lamp solution that does!

item.title: Shipping & Returns
item.dc:creator: LedLamp-Direct
item.content:encoded:
Our Shipping Policy

Our warehouse processes shipments from Monday Friday, 8am 4pm CST/CDT. Next Day Air and Second Day Air orders must be placed by 3:30pm CST/CDT. We currently ship only within the United States. Cost for shipping is based on the calculated weight of your shipment via standard ground shipping. Most orders ship within 24 hours from the time they are placed. While we work to ship an order the same day it is received, we cannot guarantee actual delivery time. Upon receipt of a valid email address for an order, we send an email with order update, when the order has shipped and package tracking information.

Return Policy

Returns are accepted for 30 days after an item has been invoiced, provided the item is unused and can be returned in its original condition.To return a product, please email info@ledlamps-direct.com with your invoice number and a phone number where you can be reached. Upon contact, you will be given a Return Material Authorization (RMA) number and shipping information. Upon product receipt and inspection, you will be notified of return status. If the returned product is accepted, the original purchase price will be refunded. If return is not accepted, the item will be returned to the shipper at the shippers cost.Typical reasons for rejecting a returned product: the product has been used; the product is damaged; or the product was not in its original condition. Please allow up to 30 days for return process.

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: LedLamp-Direct
item.content:encoded:
We respect and are committed to protecting your privacy.

What information do we collect?

Typically, we collect non-personally-identifying information of the sort that web browsers and servers typically make available, such as the browser type, language preference, referring site, and the date and time of each visitor request. The purpose in collecting non-personally-identifying information is to better understand how our visitors use its website. Personally identifiable information may be collected by our servers from your browser including your IP address and pages visited.

How is your information used?

Any of the information we collect may be used in the following ways:
  • To personalize your experience and respond to individual needs
  • To improve our website We continually strive to improve our site based on the information and feedback we receive from you.
  • To improve customer service Your information helps us respond to customer service requests and support needs more effectively .
  • To process transactions Your information, whether public or private, will not be sold, exchanged, transferred, or given to any other company for any reason, without your consent, other than for the expressed purpose of delivering the purchased product or service requested by the customer.
  • To send periodic emails The email address you provide may be used to send you information and updates pertaining to your order, in addition to receiving occasional company news, updates, related products or service information, etc. NOTE: If you would like to unsubscribe from receiving future emails, we include unsubscribe instructions at the bottom of each email.

How do we protect your information?

We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. Reference our Security Information below.

Do we disclose any information to outside parties?

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personally identifiable information to outside parties . This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in operating our website, conducting our business, or servicing you, so long as those parties agree to keep this information confidential. We may also release your information when we believe release is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect ours or others rights, property or safety. However, non-personally identifiable visitor information may be provided to other parties for marketing, advertising or other uses.

Security Information

All sensitive information entered during customer registration or during the checkout process istransferred via secure HTTPS protocol and stored on secureAmazon EC2 servers. Actual payment and collection of credit card information will take place on PayPal's website which automatically encrypts your confidential information in transit from your computer using the Secure Sockets Layer protocol (SSL) with an encryption key length of 128-bits (the highest level commercially available).
